  <summary>9/7/2000--Introduced.
NOAA Chesapeake Bay Office Improvement Act - Amends the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Authorization Act of 1992 to: (1) rename the Chesapeake Bay Estuarine Resources Office as the Chesapeake Bay Office (the Office); (2) revise the functions of the Office; (3) require a five-year study concerning living resources of the Chesapeake Bay and a multiple species management strategy for the Chesapeake Bay; (4) require a community-based fishery and habitat restoration small grants and technical assistance program in the Chesapeake Bay watershed; and (5) authorize appropriations for the Office through FY 2004.</summary>
